{"tid":1801452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「拜託給我水喝」！野火恐30%樹熊慘死  路邊攔人求救","createTime":"2019-12-28T15:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T02:56:53.000Z","uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6e413d84aa472d79a647f96e7b10740fe4f5e7","tid":1801452,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1577515349-2f526fa8727e22b1342e120077bee117.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1577515349-2f526fa8727e22b1342e120077bee117.png&h=23e11095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲澳洲 1 名自行車友，近日外出運動時，罕見遇到無尾熊求救討水喝的狀況。（圖／擷取自 IG 影片）<br />\n<br />\n澳洲野火燒不停，攪擾當地人畜不安，不只居民住家安全受威脅，大量野生動物棲息地也遭破壞，上千隻無尾熊被活活燒死，近日更有澳洲網友捕捉到無尾熊頂著高溫攔路人討水喝，讓人看了相當心疼。<br />\n<br />\n根據澳洲《 7 News 》報導，1 名自行車車友安娜赫斯勒（ Anna Heusler ）近日在個人 IG 上分享 1 段影片，她與朋友騎車行經 1 處道路，被 1 隻遭燒傷的無尾熊攔下，還主動爬上自行車討水喝，可憐兮兮的模樣讓安娜一行人十分不忍，趕快把水壺打開倒水，而無尾熊則張口、伸出舌頭拚命舔，讓人看了非常心疼：「過去這些年我們起碼看過幾百隻無尾熊，但像這種事還是頭一遭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20191228/3847776/?from=nnfb_p&amp;utm_source=fb&amp;utm_medium=nn&amp;utm_campaign=p&amp;fbclid=IwAR3Q6hfFF9DMKJ7FqBoRfsZuDe2Qsl1MkzXmmk9hJa-ktE_M0ycoTf5qL4c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20191228%2F3847776%2F%3Ffrom%3Dnnfb_p%26utm_source%3Dfb%26utm_medium%3Dnn%26utm_campaign%3Dp%26fbclid%3DIwAR3Q6hfFF9DMKJ7FqBoRfsZuDe2Qsl1MkzXmmk9hJa-ktE_M0ycoTf5qL4c&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=67b2bfae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20191228/3847776/?from=nnfb_p&amp;utm_source=fb&amp;utm_medium=nn&amp;utm_campaign=p&amp;fbclid=IwAR3Q6hfFF9DMKJ7FqBoRfsZuDe2Qsl1MkzXmmk9hJa-ktE_M0ycoTf5qL4c</a>"},{"pid":"ba00f2a4ee96482ad08ce9983125807a47fd16df","tid":1801452,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥)<br />\n<a href=\"